description: OFFER ACCEPTED. OH CANCELED. Opportunity is literally knocking at the door to this condo! This sunny, third floor home is in the heart of South Boston just moments to shops, restaurants and the Broadway T station. Historically significant, the former Bigelow School House can now be your unique home centered in the hub. Easy access to this upper level unit via the building elevator; The home features towering ceilings and windows, hardwood floors, decorator tile bath with full tub and two generous bedrooms. The building is pet friendly and has a common BBQ/picnic area and professional management. Live with convenience because this condo has extra storage and a huge parking space right next to the building door!  No offers will be accepted with a mortgage contingency until the lender has approved the Lender Questionnaire which is attached
